ed to talk to Musk first, you don=E2=80=99t need to have any deal in place,=
 you don=E2=80=99t need to have any particular mechanism in mind to spend $=
50,000 doing it. =E2=80=9CThe guy hoped that Elon would notice and buy his =
company,=E2=80=9D sure, whatever, reasonable bet. We talked about this abov=
